---
// src/pages/type.astro
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro'
---

<Layout>
  <main class="space-y-16 px-6 py-12 max-w-6xl mx-auto">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-uiLabel tracking-wide uppercase text-aopa-dkblue">Typography Specimen</h1>

    <section class="prose prose-editorial max-w-none">
      <h2>Editorial</h2>
      <p>This is a paragraph in the <code>prose-editorial</code> variant. It uses Mercury for both headings and body, with italic and strong variants styled semantically.</p>
      <blockquote>Elegant serif styling for longform editorial content.</blockquote>
    </section>

    <section class="prose prose-magazine max-w-none">
      <h2>Magazine</h2>
      <p>This variant uses Gotham Book for body, Knockout for headings, and Gotham Bold for strong. Ideal for clean, modern layouts.</p>
      <blockquote>Voice and contrast through font pairing.</blockquote>
    </section>

    <section class="prose prose-feature max-w-none">
      <h2>Feature</h2>
      <p>Designed for drama and display. Knockout all-caps headings, Gotham body, with expressive scale and spacing.</p>
      <blockquote>Front-of-book punch, back-of-book rhythm.</blockquote>
    </section>
  </main>
</Layout>
